About:

    This is a repo chiefly for storing experimental stuff.
    It is divided into following sub-sections:

    boost_unicode:

        Tutorial demonstrating how to encode/decode unicode using boost utf8_codecvt_facet.hpp

References:

    boost_unicode:

        http://www.edobashira.com/2010/03/using-boost-code-facet-for-reading-utf8.html
        http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_46_1/libs/serialization/doc/codecvt.html

Other Sources:

